The '''''Imperial Defense Daily''''', or '''''IDD''''', was a daily newsfeed service for those interested in the [[Imperial Military/Legends|Imperial Military]]. It profiled spacecraft and weapons systems as they became declassified, and was thus very popular among weapons enthusiasts. An example of this was when the ''IDD'' were the first to provide coverage of the [[Storm commando/Legends|Storm Commando]], describing their equipment, training, and future missions.

